column5: LOOKING TO BOOK A TRIP.HAS ANYONE BEEN THERE? WHATS THE CAMP LIKE AND THE FISHING.THANKS (WALLI 1)

I have never stayed there before but I have seen this Cabin from the outside and it appears to be a very nice place. I was thinking about staying there sometime but heard the price is high. If you can let me know what the rate is for staying there.
THE PRICE IS $560.00 A WEAK PER PERSON.DID YOU FISH FROM THE CAMP GROUND OR THE LODGE.

We stay at the campground I have been there the last two years and the fishing for walleye and smallmouth have been great we take our own boats. We are going to be up there Aug 3-10 If you want you can email me at [email protected]
